These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, cola, fanta, 7up, iced-tea, sprite
 1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking 7up##7
 3. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking juice##7
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 6. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
10. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Beverage   | 7up | juice | tea | cola | fanta | iced-tea | sprite |

