.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, tomato, papaya, plum, pineapple, broccoli, garlic
 1. the person eating broccoli is the person eating broccoli##1
 2. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the person eating cranberry##5
 3. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
 4. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
 6. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 9. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
10. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Food   | plum | tomato | broccoli | garlic | papaya | cranberry | pineapple |

