.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, vegafina, old-henry, aristoff, montecristo, bluemaster, dunhill
 1. the aristoff-smoker is not to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##8
 2. the dunhill-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
 4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 6. the dunhill-smoker is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8
 7. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere between the bluemaster-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##7
 8. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
10. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar   | montecristo | bluemaster | aristoff | dunhill | prince | old-henry | vegafina |

