.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, fish, goat, rat, ferret, cat
 1. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the rabbit##7
 2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the owner of the rabbit##7
 5. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the goat##7
 6. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the cat##7
 7. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
 8. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 9. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
10. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Pet   | fish | bird | goat | cat | rat | rabbit | ferret |

