3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
5. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
9. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Transport   | trike | bus | subway | helicopter | snowmobile | roller | quad-bike |

