 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching satire movies##7
 8. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
 9. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
