 9. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
10. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
11. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
12. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing chess##1
